Package: easyNRD
Title: Tidy Tools for HCUP Nationwide Readmissions Database Workflows
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ali", "Salman", email = "alisalman.et.al@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides composable, lazy-evaluation friendly tools for cleaning,
    episode consolidation, and readmission linkage in Healthcare Cost and
    Utilization Project Nationwide Readmissions Database (HCUP-NRD) data.
    Functions are designed for Arrow and DuckDB backends to support large,
    out-of-core analytic pipelines and denominator-preserving survival methods,
    including competing-risk frameworks.
